name: Dream
description:
Some people believe that it all begins with a dream.
When I glance up, it appears to be so close yet so far away.

I make an effort to reach out, but I've come to recognize something.
It is not due to the distance, but rather to the fact that
It's my hand that can't reach it.

I'll keep on reaching out till my hand reaches its maximum length.
I'll be able to get there by that time.
